  m_text: 'Run Info:

    Each tile has a base value.

    Melds are collections
    of 2 or more of the same tile.

    If it is part of a meld, each tile''s value
    is multipied by the tiles in the meld.

    Flowers and Seasons are bonus points.

    Eyes
    - 2x

    Pung - 3x

    Kong - 4x

    Chow - 5x

    ...so forth.'
